<para style="p">For the chief musician; set to Jonath elem rehokim. A psalmof David. A michtam; when the Philistines took him in Gath.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Be merciful to me, God, for men are attacking me!</para>

<para style="q1">All the day long those who fight me press their assault.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />My enemies trample me all day long;</para>

<para style="q1">for there are many who arrogantly fight against me.</para>
